Directed by Robert Quinn.

Written by Michael Crompton. Michael Crompton. T.M. Logan. T.M. Logan.

Cast Aneurin Barnard (Ryan). Poppy Gilbert (Abbie). Cathy Belton (Claire). Ian Pirie (Bob). Morgan Palmeria (George). Jade Jordan (Katz). Brenda Fricker (Phyllis). Jacob Hickey (Josh). Menyee Lai (Pauline). Paul Sparkes (Wayne Pendrick). Karl Hogan (Baxter). Tracy Wiles (D.I Jennie Nott). Cameron Jack (Craig)

Language English.

Producers Larry Bass. Stuart Cheetham. Glen Collins. Michael Crompton. Trevor Eve. Aaron Farrell. Jyoti Fernandes. Rachel Gesua. Herbert Kloiber. Suzi McIntosh. John Norton. Olivia Pahl. David Swetman. Paul Testar.

Production Channel 5 Television. Night Train Media. Projector Pictures.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 4

Status OnGoing (2023–)
